data.description:
$5000 SELLER ALLOWANCE TO BE USED AS BUYER CHOOSES!!!

Very nice updated three bedroom, two bath home with garage in Cliffdale West!  Quick commute to post via I-295!  Home features formal living and dining rooms, family room, eat-in-kitchen with stainless appliances granite countertops, tile backsplash, LVP flooring, and upgraded cabinets.  Very spacious primary suite offers walk in closet, ceiling fan, chair railing, and updated bathroom with newer vanity and tile flooring! LVP flooring in dining room, living room, kitchen and family room.  NEW HVAC UNIT installed in May of 2023! Must see this affordable family home with large privacy fenced back yard!
